Class NotificationEntity

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.entity.NotificationEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class NotificationEntity extends Object implements Serializable
The NotificationEntity class represents the "notification" table in the database. Each instance of this class corresponds to a single row in the table.
